name: Stylish Extension - Dark Theme
description: Darkens the entire Stylish Extension and the Stylish Extension popup when you click on the extension in the bar to the right of the omnibox.

user.name: AlienDrew
user.about:

additional_info:
Supported Browsers:
* Chrome
* Edge
* Opera
* Brave
+ all other Chromium based browsers

Unsupported Browsers:
* Firefox: doesn't allow theming extension pages
* Safari: Stylish isn't even made for this browser
+ all other Gecko based browsers
